data.description: A charming 3-bedroom, 1-bath home in Des Moines, Iowa, awaits you! Revel in the comfort of a brand-new HVAC system and a recently installed water heater. Located near a park, this property features spacious bedrooms, a cozy bathroom, a fenced backyard for outdoor fun, and a partially finished basement for flexibility. It also offers a two-car garage for storage and a hot tub for relaxation. Don't miss this opportunity!
